                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d558">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Wilson</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Brussels</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1908-10-29">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 29, 1908</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>On Saturday, 31st, the King will create the department of colonies and appoint
                    Mr. Renkin minister for the colonies.</p>
                <p>On the same day will appear the royal decree provided in article 4 of annexation
                    treaty fixing the date of Belgian assumption of sovereignty over the Kongo.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
